Package org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson.datavalues

Class JacksonInnerTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson.datavalues.JacksonInnerTime

  • public class JacksonInnerTime
extends Object
    Helper object that represents the JSON object structure that is used to represent values of type JacksonValue.JSON_VALUE_TYPE_STRING.
    Author:
    Fredo Erxleben
